quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,90,"Fiyaake on wonaali wano Й“e nodditorta non, ko woni, Men addanii Й“e Goonga ka sikke alah e mu'un, pellelt, kamЙ“e ko fenuЙ“e e ko Й“e nodditii kon wonnde no woodani Alla kafidaaЙ—o e Й“iЙ—Й—o, Alla Toowii gaayi ngol konngol maЙ“Й“e Toowal Mawnungal."
  23,91,"Alla jogitaaki Й“iЙ—Й—o wano heeferЙ“e Й“en aaЖґori non, reweteeЙ—o e goonga kadi alah wonndude e Makko, sinndo wonno reweteeЙ—o e goonga no wonndi e Makko, reweteeЙ—o kala yaadayno e geЙ“al mu'un ngal immorde e tagu ngu o tagi ngun, yoga maЙ“Й“e foolondirayno e yoga, Й—um bonna njuЙ“Й“udi goodal ngal, ko selli kon, ko wonndema hay e huunde e Й—um waЙ—aali. Ko Й—um tinndini wonndema pellet, ReweteeЙ—o On e Goonga ko Gooto ko Kanko tun woni Alla, O Senike O LaaЙ“ii gaayi e ko sirkooЙ“e Й“en sifotoo Mo kon, kon ko haananah Mo immorde e Й“iЙ—Й—o e kafidaaЙ—o."
  23,92,"AnnduЙ—o kala ko wirnii e tagu Makko ngun, e AnnduЙ—o ko seedetee heftiree so'irЙ—e Й—en, hay e huunde e Й—um suuЙ—anaaki Mo, O Toowii Senayee wonanii Mo nde laatantoo Mo kafidaaЙ—o."
  23,93,"Maaku -Ko an yo NulaaЙ—o-: "Jooma, si A hollii lam e Й“ee sirkooЙ“e ko foduЙ—aaЙ“e kon immorde e Lepte Й—en"."
  23,94,"Joomam, pellet, battane maЙ“Й“e Й—en min miЙ—o seedii Й—um, wata A waЙ—tidam e maЙ“Й“e sakko heЙ“a lam ko heЙ“i Й“e kon immorde e Lepte Й—en."
  23,95,"Pellet, Menen ko Men HattanЙ“e nde Men waЙ—ay maa hiЙ—a yi'a seedoo ko Men fodiЙ“e kon immorde e Lepte Й—en, Men ronkatah Й—um wanaa kadi e tanaa mu'un [Men ronkata]."
  23,96,"DuГ±ir -an NulaaЙ—o- on wonЙ—o bonde e maaЙ—a geЙ“al Й“urngal moЖґЖґude ngal; Й—um woni yaafaade mo, muГ±Г±oЙ—aa e dow lorra makko kan, ko Menen Й“uri Anndunde ko Й“e woni kon sifaade immorde e sirku ngun e fennugol ngol, e ko Й“e wonumaa sifaade kon immorde e huunde nde haananaa ma, wano mbilewu e feetere."
  23,97,"Maaku: "Jooma mi rentorii Ma immorde e hodooje Seytanuuji Й—in e sonwosiyee(sikke sikke) majji"."
  23,98,"Mi moolorii Ma Jooma am nde Й—i tawata lam e nder huunde immorde e fiyakuuji am Й—in."
  23,99,"Haa si mayde nden arii goЙ—Й—o e Й“ee sirkooЙ“e, o yi'i ko woni kon jippaade e makko o wi'i hara ko o nimsuЙ—o e dow ko feЖґЖґi kon e ngurdam makko Й—am, e ko o welsindinoo kon e bannge Alla: "Jooma, ruttam faade ka ngurdam aduna"."
  23,100,"No gasa min, mi gollay ko moЖґЖґi si mi ruttike faade e makko [ka aduna]. ЖЉum waЙ—atah, fiyaake on wonaa no Й—aЙ“Й“irЙ—aa non, Й—um ko konngol tun nii, ko kanko wowlingol, hay sinndo o ruttano faade e ngurndam aduna Й—am o humnataano ko o fodi kon, Й“ee maayooЙ“e aray Й“e heddoo e nder heedo hakkonde aduna e Laakara haa Г‘alnde Immital e caakal ngal, Й“e ruttataako immorde e Й—um faade e aduna fii yo Й“e hewtito ko feЖґЖґirnoo Й“e kon, Й“e moЖґЖґintina ko Й“e bonnunoo kan."
  23,101,"Si Malaa'ikaajo fawaaЙ—o on wuttugol ka alaadu o wuttii wuttannde Й—immere nden noddaynde nden e Darngal ngal, haray dammbe alah hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Й—e Й“e wasorta Й—um, sabu hilnagol maЙ“Й“e kulol Darngal ngal, yoga maЙ“Й“e lanndoytaako yoga sabu hilnagol maЙ“Й“e ngol ko maapini Й“e kon."
  23,102,"Kala mo manndake mu'un teddiri sabu jistugol maЖґЖґi makko Й—in e dow bonЙ—i makko Й—in, haray ko Й“en woni malaaЙ“e Й“en sabu heЙ“ugol maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“i kon, e ko Й“e woЙ—Й—intee kon immorde e koЙ“e huli kon."
  23,103,"Kala mo manndake mu'un hoyi sabu jistugol bonЙ—i makko Й—in e dow moЖґЖґi makko Й—in haray Й“en Й—on ko kamЙ“e woni yeebirЙ“e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in sabu gollugol ko lorrata Й—i kon, e Й—alugol ko nafata Й—i kon immorde e gomЙ—inal e golle moЖґЖґe, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e Г±iiЙ“ooЙ“e ka Yiite Jahannama, Й“e yaltatah e magge."
  23,104,"Yiite ngen no sunna geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hara kamЙ“e e nder magge, toni maЙ“Й“e dowji Й—in e leyji Й—in tagginoke gaayi Г±iiЖґe maЙ“Й“e Й—en immorde e saЙ—tude Г±irЙ“inagol."